      "text": [
        "218 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «اَلْمَبْطُونُ وَ اَلْكَسِيرُ يُؤَمَّمَانِ وَ لاَ يُغَسَّلاَنِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.218 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n'One who is suffering from a severe stomach illness or has broken bones should perform tayammum and should not perform ghusl (ritual bathing).'."
        ]
      }
    }
  },
